                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="7" rotate="0" align="center">
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">NO-OUT OF SPEC.</emph>
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody valign="top">
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="1" rotate="0">
                                <para>1.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="2" rotate="0">
                                <para>Off/On</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="3" rotate="0">
                                <para>During the gauge sweep all LCD elements of the display should be activated and the
                                    backlighting should illuminate.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="5" rotate="0">
                                <para>Display elements are active and backlights work during gauge sweep.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="6" rotate="0">
                                <para>Digital display is working. If problems continue, replace EGC circuit board.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="7" rotate="0">
                                <para>Replace LCD display.</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                    </tbody>
                </tgroup>
            </table>
        </svcsubproc>
